javax.security.identitystore.annotation

Annotation Type Validator


  • @Qualifier
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD,FIELD,PARAMETER})
 @Repeatable(value=Validators.class)
public @interface Validator
    Validator is a CDI Qualifier, which registers CredentialValidator implementations for use by IdentityStore, to validate a Credential implementation against an IdentityStore implementation.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      Class<? extends Credential> credentialClass 
      Class<? extends IdentityStore> identityStoreClass
